		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Plan a Results to Action workshop, where you will bring government agencies, local organizations, and residents together to brainstorm and evaluate actions to address the equity and resilience issues identified in the Assess section.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
				<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Involving community participants in identifying actions that can be taken to address equitable resilience issues is critical to making sure actions will meet the needs of the community.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
				<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Get together with your core team and review the Reflection Diary to build on what worked in previous workshops, especially for reducing barriers to participation.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Review your goals from your Project Plan and define objectives for the workshop to meet your goals.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Review the workshop activities described in the rest of this section and use the Results to Action Workshop Agenda Builder to select the activities you plan to include to meet your objectives.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Review the Facilitators Guide for Workshops and Results to Action Workshop Sample Agenda Workshop and design your workshop agenda.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Coordinate with any other local partners necessary to address the Action Areas the workshop will focus on.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
